# üéØ **EXAM MEIN ZARUR AANE WALE COMMANDS**

---

## ‚≠ê **CATEGORY 1: BASIC COMMANDS (100% POOCHA JAYEGA)**

### **Must Know - Har Exam Mein Hote Hain**

| Command | Purpose | Marks Worth | Example Answer |
|---------|---------|-------------|----------------|
| `claude` | Start Claude Code | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Claude Code ko start karne ke liye current project folder mein `claude` command use karte hain |
| `/exit` | Exit/Quit | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | Claude Code se exit karne ke liye `/exit` ya `/quit` use karte hain |
| `/help` | Show all commands | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Available commands ki list dekhne ke liye `/help` command use hoti hai |
| `/reset` | Clear conversation | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | Conversation history clear karne ke liye `/reset` command use karte hain |
| `/list` | Show files | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Current directory ki files dekhne ke liye `/list` ya `/ls` command |

---

## ‚≠ê‚≠ê **CATEGORY 2: FILE OPERATIONS (80% CHANCES)**

### **File Management - Important Topic**

| Command | Purpose | Marks Worth | Key Points for Answer |
|---------|---------|-------------|------------------------|
| `/new` | Create new file | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Syntax: `/new filename.ext` <br> Example: `/new app.js` |
| `/edit` | Edit existing file | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Existing file ko modify karne ke liye <br> Syntax: `/edit filename.ext` |
| `/read` | View file content | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | File ka content dekhne ke liye <br> Syntax: `/read filename.ext` |
| `/delete` | Remove file | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | File delete karne ke liye <br> Warning: Permanent delete |
| `/save` | Save changes | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Current changes save karne ke liye |

**Exam Tip:** File operations ke sath hamesha example dena!

