## ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê **CATEGORY 3: PROJECT COMMANDS (90% CHANCES)**

### **Project Management - High Priority**

| Command | Purpose | Marks Worth | Interview Answer Template |
|---------|---------|-------------|---------------------------|
| `/init` | Initialize project | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Naya project setup karne ke liye `/init` command use karte hain. Example: `/init react` se React project initialize hota hai" |
| `/install` | Install packages | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "npm packages install karne ke liye. Syntax: `/install package-name`. Example: `/install express`" |
| `/run` | Execute project | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Project ko run karne ke liye `/run` command. Development server start hota hai" |
| `/build` | Build for production | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Production build banane ke liye. Optimized code generate hoti hai" |
| `/test` | Run tests | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Test cases run karne ke liye `/test` command use hoti hai" |

**Exam Tip:** Har command ke sath use case batana zaruri hai!

