## ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê **CATEGORY 4: GIT COMMANDS (70% CHANCES)**

### **Version Control - Popular Questions**

| Command | Purpose | Marks Worth | Expected Answer |
|---------|---------|-------------|-----------------|
| `/git init` | Initialize Git | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Git repository initialize karne ke liye. Project mein version control setup hota hai" |
| `/git add .` | Stage all files | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Sabhi files ko staging area mein add karne ke liye. Commit ke liye ready" |
| `/commit` | Save changes | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Changes ko Git history mein save karne ke liye. Syntax: `/commit 'message'`" |
| `/push` | Upload to remote | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Local changes ko remote repository (GitHub) pe upload karne ke liye" |
| `/branch` | Create branch | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | "Naya branch banane ke liye. Syntax: `/branch branch-name`" |

**Exam Tip:** Git workflow explain kar sake to bonus marks!

